# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

[[screens]]
id = "xray_knee"
name = "Knee X-Ray"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 0
  label = "Normal"
  action = "text"
  content = """AP, lateral, and sunrise views of the left knee.

Normal alignment and mineralization. No fracture or dislocation.
Joint spaces preserved (medial, lateral, patellofemoral). No
effusion. No loose bodies. Soft tissues unremarkable.

IMPRESSION: Normal left knee radiographs."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 1
  label = "OA Medial"
  action = "text"
  content = """AP and lateral views of the right knee, weight-bearing.

Moderate medial compartment joint space narrowing with subchondral
sclerosis and marginal osteophytes. Lateral compartment and PFJ
relatively preserved. No fracture or effusion.

IMPRESSION: Moderate medial compartment osteoarthritis. KL grade 3."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 2
  label = "OA Tricomp"
  action = "text"
  content = """AP, lateral, and sunrise views of the right knee.

Severe tricompartmental joint space narrowing with pronounced
subchondral sclerosis, subchondral cysts, and large osteophytes.
Varus malalignment.

IMPRESSION: Severe tricompartmental OA. KL grade 4 with varus
deformity. Orthopedic evaluation for arthroplasty."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 0
  label = "SLine"
  action = "select_line"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 1
  label = "LStart"
  action = "line_start"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 2
  label = "LEnd"
  action = "line_end"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 3
  label = "Del"
  action = "delete"
