# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# xray_hand_metacarp — Metacarpal Fracture
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

[[screens]]
id = "xray_hand_metacarp"
name = "Metacarpal Fracture"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 0
  label = "Boxer Fx"
  action = "text"
  content = """PA, oblique, and lateral views of the right hand.

Impacted transverse fracture through fifth metacarpal neck with ~35
degrees volar angulation. No intra-articular extension or rotational
deformity. Remaining metacarpals and phalanges unremarkable.

IMPRESSION: Fifth MC neck fracture (boxer fracture) with moderate
volar angulation. Closed reduction if > 40 degrees."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 1
  label = "Bennett"
  action = "text"
  content = """PA and lateral views of the right thumb.

Oblique intra-articular fracture through first MC base with ~2 mm
displacement and radial/dorsal subluxation of MC shaft. Volar-ulnar
fragment attached to anterior oblique ligament.

IMPRESSION: Bennett fracture with CMC subluxation. Unstable injury.
Urgent orthopedic referral for CRPP or ORIF."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 2
  label = "Rolando"
  action = "text"
  content = """PA and lateral views of the left thumb.

Comminuted, Y-shaped intra-articular fracture through first MC base
with multiple displaced fragments involving both articular surfaces.
Significant joint incongruity.

IMPRESSION: Rolando fracture (comminuted first MC base). Urgent hand
surgery referral for ORIF or external fixation."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 0
  label = "SLine"
  action = "select_line"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 1
  label = "LStart"
  action = "line_start"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 2
  label = "LEnd"
  action = "line_end"
  [[screens.buttons]]
