Liver, gallbladder, spleen, pancreas, adrenals, and kidneys normal in
size, contour, and enhancement. No focal lesions. Normal bowel caliber.
No free fluid or free air. No lymphadenopathy. Bladder and pelvic
organs unremarkable.

IMPRESSION: Normal contrast-enhanced CT abdomen and pelvis."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 1
  label = "Appendicitis"
  action = "text"
  content = """CT of abdomen and pelvis with IV contrast.

Appendix dilated (12 mm) with wall enhancement, periappendiceal fat
stranding, and small appendicolith at tip. Minimal adjacent free fluid.
No abscess or perforation. Remainder unremarkable.

IMPRESSION: Acute appendicitis with appendicolith. No perforation.
Surgical consultation recommended."""
