  content = """Non-contrast chest CT for nodule follow-up.

Solid pulmonary nodule measuring 6 x 5 mm in RUL (series 2, image 45).
No calcification or fat. Stable compared to prior study of <date>. No
new nodules.

IMPRESSION: Stable 6 mm solid nodule, RUL. Follow-up in 12 months per
Fleischner guidelines."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 1
  label = "Solid >8mm"
  action = "text"
  content = """Non-contrast chest CT for nodule evaluation.

Solid pulmonary nodule measuring 11 x 9 mm with lobulated margins in
LLL (series 2, image 67). No calcification. Mild surrounding GGO. No
other nodules. Mediastinal and hilar nodes normal.

IMPRESSION: 11 mm solid nodule, LLL, indeterminate. PET/CT or tissue
sampling per Fleischner. Short-term follow-up (3 months) alternative
for low-risk patients."""
