# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# mri_spine_lumbar_stenosis — Lumbar Stenosis
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

[[screens]]
id = "mri_spine_lumbar_stenosis"
name = "Lumbar Stenosis"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 0
  label = "Central"
  action = "text"
  content = """MRI of the lumbar spine without contrast.

Severe central spinal canal stenosis at L3-L4 and L4-L5 secondary to
broad-based disc bulges, ligamentum flavum hypertrophy, and facet OA.
Thecal sac AP diameter 6 mm at L4-L5. Crowding of cauda equina.
Multilevel moderate foraminal narrowing.

IMPRESSION: Severe multilevel central canal stenosis (L3-L5) with
cauda equina crowding. Neurosurgical decompressive laminectomy."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 0
  col = 1
  label = "Foraminal"
  action = "text"
  content = """MRI of the lumbar spine without contrast.

Moderate to severe bilateral neural foraminal narrowing at L4-L5 and
L5-S1 due to disc height loss, uncovertebral/facet hypertrophy, and
posterolateral disc bulges. Exiting L4, L5, and S1 nerve roots contacted
bilaterally. No significant central stenosis.

IMPRESSION: Multilevel foraminal stenosis with bilateral nerve root
contact. Pain management for selective nerve root blocks."""
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 0
  label = "SLine"
  action = "select_line"
  [[screens.buttons]]
  row = 4
  col = 1
  label = "LStart"
  action = "line_start"
